s</span>\n          <span class=\"sql-chip\">CTEs</span>\n        </div>\n        <a class=\"sql-link\" href=\"https://github.com/rsm-joz021/8-SQL-Challenges/tree/main/Case%20Study%20%232%20-%20Pizza%20Runner\" target=\"_blank\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation()\">View Solution ↗</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"sql-card\" onclick=\"toggleSQL(this)\">\n    <div class=\"sql-card-header\">\n      <span class=\"sql-case-badge\">Case 3</span>\n      <span class=\"sql-emoji\">🥑</span>\n      <div class=\"sql-title-block\">\n        <h3>Foodie-Fi</h3>\n        <p class=\"sql-subtitle\">Subscription analytics</p>\n      </div>\n      <span class=\"sql-chevron\">▸</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"sql-card-details\">\n      <div class=\"sql-card-details-inner\">\n        <p class=\"sql-desc\">Track plan upgrades, downgrades, and churn for a streaming service; model payment schedules and forecast business outcomes.</p>\n        <div class=\"sql-chips\">\n          <span class=\"sql-chip\">Date Functions</span>\n          <span class=\"sql-chip\">CASE WHEN</span>\n          <span class=\"sql-chip\">Window Functions</span>\n          <span class=\"sql-chip\">Churn Analysis</span>\n        </div>\n        <a class=\"sql-link\" href=\"https://github.com/rsm-joz021/8-SQL-Challenges/tree/main/Case%20Study%20%233%20-%20Foodie-Fi\" target=\"_blank\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation()\">View Solution ↗</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"sql-card\" onclick=\"toggleSQL(this)\">\n    <div class=\"sql-card-header\">\n      <span class=\"sql-case-badge\">Case 4</span>\n      <span class=\"sql-emoji\">🏦</span>\n      <div class=\"sql-title-block\">\n        <h3>Data Bank</h3>\n        <p class=\"sql-subtitle\">Digital banking data</p>\n      </div>\n      <span class=\"sql-chevron\">▸</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"sql-card-details\">\n      <div class=\"sql-card-details-inner\">\n        <p class=\"sql-desc\">Map customer nodes acros